caption: A woman stands gracefully in a lush, green meadow, her back turned as she gazes into the distance. She holds a vibrant bouquet of sunflowers in one hand, while the other gently secures her straw hat against the playful breeze. Around her, delicate bubbles drift and dance in the wind, catching the light and creating a whimsical atmosphere. The scene is serene and enchanting, with the bubbles reflecting the surrounding greenery and adding a touch of magic to the tranquil setting.
